Auction: On site, Thursday 21st June 2012 at 10.00 am

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: One minute drive to M1 Pacific Motorway

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are proud to the present 9 Lacy Court Carrara. The newest industrial unit complex which is on track to be completed in late 2021.

These high quality units are centrally located along the M1 Motorway between Nerang and Burleigh Heads.

If your business requires high clearance warehousing, easy access to the M1 Motorway, a good corporate image and good car parking for staff then this estate is a must see for any business.

The development features:

• Units starts from $757,100 + GST
• 12 units from 240m² to 528m²
• Prime location in Carrara with quick access to the M1 Pacific Motorway
• Easy truck access for entering, exiting, turning, loading and unloading ability
• Dedicated container set down loading bay
• Access to 3 phase power
• Excellent on-site parking for each unit
• Container high roll doors
• High quality concrete mezzanine flooring
• Flexible fit-out options
• Completion due late 2021

For more information and inspection please contact the exclusive marketing agent Luke Brechin and David Corke today.

CBRE are pleased present the exciting investment opportunity at 3-5 Ryecroft Street, Carrara which includes a secure long term lease to a well Established National Business. 

The property is being SOLD via and expressions of interest campaign which closes on the 1st September 2021 at 4pm. 

The opportunity features:

-	Annual income of $198,480 net + outgoings + GST
-	Secure 10 year lease with options
-	1,644sqm of office / warehouse area on 3,048sqm of land 
-	Block and Metal Clad construction warehouse 
-	Well presented offices and showroom area
-	Medium impact zoning  
-	350m to M1 Motorway at exit 77 
-	Centrally located on the Gold Coast between Burleigh Heads & Nerang 

If you would like to know more information on this assess or arrange and inspection please contact your exclusive agents CBRE.
